data.description: You'll love this great home in Pelican Point. Remodeled kitchen featuring concrete breakfast bar, butcher block counters, white subway tiles, and top-of-line stainless steel appliances. The sunroom flexes as an office/breakfast nook. Vaulted ceilings, a cozy wood-burning fireplace in the sunken living room. The primary suite includes a full bath & walk-in closet. The hall bath has a really nice walk-in shower. The backyard is private, fully fenced w/underground sprinklers, a large deck, tall trees & mature landscaping.  Entertain around the firepit while keeping an eye on the fun in the tree house.  Boat/RV parking beside the driveway & there's a shop behind the garage for lawn tools. It's a great location w/ a community park & boat launch!
